turn.4: This power allows him to essentially teleport between any two dark areas.
turn.5: What did he do with this power?
turn.6: He uses this power to rescue his abusive father, who was trapped in a mine, but his father later accuses him of being in league with the Devil.
turn.7: Is there anything else of note?
turn.8: In his rage, Boxer's father attacked his wife, causing her to miscarry her unborn child.
turn.9: Was the father punished for this?
turn.10: Boxer killed his father as retribution.
turn.11: Are there any other interesting aspects about this article?
turn.12: As an adult in Bete Noire, Shadow Boxer acts as Doctor Juris's main enforcer.
